songs.title: Kickback
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Kick-Kickback..

[Verse 1]
Got a white bitch, love to ride on the dick (ride, ride)
Then I got a Spanish bitch, let her ride during licks (she wanna die)
And she from the Agg', gotta watch out who she with
'Cause it's opps out there, and I been hittin' licks (hm)

[Chorus]
Kickback, kickback, choppa, it's gon' kickback
Choppa, it go click-clack, I'm lookin' for the piss pack (Rug-Rat!)
Kickback, kickback (baow), Glock, it's gon' kickback (baow, baow)
Choppa, it go click-clack I'm lookin' for the piss pack

[Verse 2]
Fullback, pull that
Run up like a fullback (run up, nigga)
Why you pull your gun out?
Now you can't get your tool back (gimme yo' tool)
Tay-K, they know me, got shooters on my balcony
A nigga run up in this hoe, it's gon' be a fatality (he dead)
Your bitch wan' get serious, she tryna get a house with me (no)
Bitch, icecream on my feet, but ain't shit sweet about me (no)

[Chorus]
Kickback, kickback, choppa, it's gon' kickback
Choppa, it go click-clack, I'm lookin' for the piss pack (Rug-Rat)
Kickback, kickback, Glock, it's gon' kickback
